title: Diary of the Dead 2007 (MJhermit)
description:
George Ramero: Diary of the Dead (2007)


  A group of film production students visiting the countryside to film a zombie film, realize fiction will will become fact as reports of the dead re-animating come over radio and television. The students decide to make a online blog about the events unfolding for main stream media is down playiong the situation and killing thousands by day. It's now the responsibilty of kids, you know teenagers, bloggers to be the trusted media and get the word out
